		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T6A</code>: Experience Reports</h1>
		Work that primarily reports practical experience, be it academic or industrial. Lessons learnt from building and using software languages, long-term maintenance experiences, pedagogical practice reports, and reflective case narratives. If the paper contributes a wider applicable technique while using experience in its use as validation, we tag that technique as primary.
